<div class="warnings">
<div class="warning js-warning" data-code="CORONAVIRUS_BORDER">
<span class="header">COVID-19</span>
<div class="warning-msg">Montenegro has allowed entry on all border
crossings to nationals and foreign travelers without having a test for COVID-19. Travelers originating from the UK must have a medical certificate with a negative COVID-19 PCR test result issued within 72 hours prior to arrival.</div>
<a class="js-link js-modal-trigger" href="javascript:void(0)" aria-label="Learn more">
Learn more
</a>
</div>

<div id="c5DEx-query-alerts-dialog" class="Common-Widgets-Dialog-Dialog R9-Overlay a11y-focus-outlines extraRadius fromTop" role="alertdialog" tabindex="-1" data-dialog-owner="c5DEx" aria-modal="true">
<div id="c5DEx-query-alerts-dialog-focusStartBoundary" class="last-focusable off-screen" tabindex="0"></div>
<div id="c5DEx-query-alerts-dialog-modal" class="modalBackground">
</div>
<div id="c5DEx-query-alerts-dialog-viewport" class="viewport">
<div id="c5DEx-query-alerts-dialog-content" class="content ">
<button id="c5DEx-query-alerts-dialog-close" class="Button-No-Standard-Style close darkIcon " aria-label="Close">
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 9.85 9.93" class="x-icon-x " aria-hidden="true"><use xlink:href="#-images-horizon-common-icon-x-icon"></use></svg> </button>
<div id="c5DEx-query-alerts-dialog-body" class="body">
<div class="Flights-Results-FlightQueryAlerts-dialog">
<b id="entryRestrictions">Entry restrictions</b><p>Montenegro has allowed entry on all border
<br>crossings to nationals and foreign travelers without having a test for COVID-19 with observance of health measures, in accordance with health warning of the Institute. However, Montenegro is imposing pre-travel testing requirements for travelers arriving from the UK.
<br></p><b id="entryRequirements">Entry requirements</b><p>Travelers originating from the UK, France, Portugal, Spain, Denmark, Netherlands, Ireland, Belgium, Czech Republic, Israel, Malta, Lithuania, Estonia, Latvia, US, Brazil, South Africa, India, Bahrain, Lebanon, Luxembourg, San Marino, Botswana, Andorra, Slovakia and Bulgaria must have a medical certificate with a negative COVID-19 PCR test result issued within 72 hours prior to arrival. 
<br>
<br>
<br>Travelers arriving from elsewhere, including UK citizens, can enter Montenegro without a COVID-19 test through all border crossings.</p><b id="quarantineRequirements">Quarantine requirements</b><p>Nationals and residents of Montenegro arriving from the UK, France, Portugal, Spain, Denmark, Netherlands, Ireland, Belgium, Czech Republic, Israel, Malta, Lithuania, Estonia, Latvia, US, Brazil, South Africa, India, Bahrain, Lebanon, Luxembourg, San Marino, Botswana, Andorra, Slovakia and Bulgaria can enter without a medical certificate with a negative COVID-19 PCR test result issued within 72 hours prior to arrival but are subject to self-isolation for 14 days.</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="c5DEx-query-alerts-dialog-focusEndBoundary" class="last-focusable off-screen" tabindex="0"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<section id="Dsqn-details-rates" class="details-section bookingSection" role="tabpanel" data-tab="rates" aria-expanded="true">
<div id="c_ima" class="Flights-Results-FlightRatesTable Flights-Results-FlightRatesTableV3">

try {
log.time("init");
var deferred = document.querySelectorAll("link[data-rel='stylesheet']");

R9.devupdate.update();
}
initComplete = true;
} finally {
log.timeEnd("init");
}
try {

R9.events.ready("page.initialized");
} finally {
log.timeEnd("page.initialized");
}
}

}
